    <content>&lt;P&gt;The service plan that I can see in theEntitlements of my Free Tier SAP Partner subaccount&amp;nbsp; is called dev:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="gregorw_0-1736066038124.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/207579i0C3B4EAA75228C6A/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="gregorw_0-1736066038124.png" alt="gregorw_0-1736066038124.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;According to the SAP Discovery center entry for&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://discovery-center.cloud.sap/serviceCatalog/cloud-logging?service_plan=overall-(large,-standard,-and-dev)&amp;amp;region=all&amp;amp;commercialModel=btpea&amp;amp;tab=service_plan" target="_self" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP Cloud Logging&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;there is no lite plan. I've also checked if I could assign Cloud Logging in my BTP Trial. But it's not even there:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="gregorw_1-1736066187606.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/207580i451DB83A2864E7E3/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="gregorw_1-1736066187606.png" alt="gregorw_1-1736066187606.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I hope that someone responsible for Cloud Logging from SAP will help to close this gap.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
